column3: Oh. Oh my god. I forgot to ask your name.
It's all good.  Call me Dreamwalker
Huh. What are you doing around here?
Ehh. Everyone says that, but I don't really see it myself.

There's something about fungi that creeps me out. Always has. It's almost parasitic. Feeds off of death. I know it's an important part of the ecosystem, but truth be told, I can't bring myself to like it.
You don't need to stay if it creeps you out.
What do you mean? I'm your sister. Through thick and thin, right? I'm not going until you're ready.
You want me to leave this place??
Wake up wake up wake up wake up wake up wake up wake up wake up wake up wake up wake up wake up wake up wake up wake up wake up wake up wake up.
The water is as red as blood yet no blood has been spilt.
